[
    {
        "source_sentence": "大般涅槃經集解卷第三十七",
        "translation": "Mahāparinirvāṇa-sūtra, Collected and Explained, Volume 37",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0496c17_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　明慈悲有實益",
        "translation": "to clarify that compassion is truly beneficial",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0496c19_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　廣明慈心中布施發願事",
        "translation": "vow for the widespread dissemination of alms in the mind of compassion",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0496c20_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　廣明菩薩所脩之慈即萬行",
        "translation": "explain in detail that the compassion cultivated by the bodhisattvas is the myriad practices",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0496c21_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　廣明慈益象見師子力士移石盧至長者斯那大多女人及提婆達多憍薩羅賊流離太子梵行品之第二迦葉菩薩白佛言世尊(至)如是之觀非虛妄耶。",
        "translation": "Guangming Ciyi Xiang saw Shizi Lüshi Lu to the elder Snaduo Dātuo and Devadatta Kauśālapati, the second of the Brahma Chapter of Prince Lüe, and Kāśyapa said to the Buddha, \"Bhagavān, is this observation not false?",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0496c22_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "案。",
        "translation": "Commentary.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0496c27_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "僧亮曰。",
        "translation": "Sengliang said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0496c27_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第三門明四等。",
        "translation": "'The third approach explains the four levels.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0496c27_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是實行也。",
        "translation": "It's also a practice.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0496c27_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "難有兩意。",
        "translation": "It's difficult to have two meanings.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0496c27_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此以虛行為難也。",
        "translation": "This refers to the difficulty of practicing in vain.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0496c28_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "僧宗曰。",
        "translation": "Saṃgha Zong said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0496c28_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "難有三重。",
        "translation": "'There are three levels of difficulty.'",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0496c28_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此初重云。",
        "translation": "The first one is this.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0496c29_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "眾生在苦。",
        "translation": "'Sentient beings are in suffering.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0496c29_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不蒙救拔。",
        "translation": "They aren't rescued.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0496c29_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "證慈非實也。",
        "translation": "It proves that compassion isn't real.'",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0496c29_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "寶亮曰。",
        "translation": "Baoliang said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a01_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此下大段之第三也。",
        "translation": "\"This is the third of the following major sections.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a01_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "明慈是實行。",
        "translation": "It explains that kindness is practiced.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a01_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "將辨此理故。",
        "translation": "It's because we'll explain this principle.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a01_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦葉先作虛妄之難也。",
        "translation": "Kāśyapa first made it a false objection.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a02_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此中凡六翻。",
        "translation": "There are six explanations of this.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a02_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此下第一釋慈體是實行。",
        "translation": "The first one below explains that the essence of kindness is its practice.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a03_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦葉引五事。",
        "translation": "Kāśyapa cites five things.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a03_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "證其無實之難也。",
        "translation": "It's a realization of the difficulty of not being real.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a03_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊若非虛妄實與樂者(至)威德力故一切受樂。",
        "translation": "\"Bhagavān, if it's not false and really gives pleasure, then all [sentient beings] will experience pleasure because of the power of his might.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a05_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "案。",
        "translation": "Commentary.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a06_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "僧宗曰。",
        "translation": "The Saṃgha School says.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a06_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第二重難。",
        "translation": "\"The second serious difficulty is this.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a06_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如其必益。",
        "translation": "As it is, it's bound to be beneficial.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a06_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是則眾生必應離苦也。",
        "translation": "Then sentient beings surely will part with suffering.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a06_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若當真實不得樂者(至)云何得與此義相應。",
        "translation": "If it's true that they won't attain happiness, then how can they conform to this meaning?",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a08_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "案。",
        "translation": "Commentary.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a09_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "僧亮曰。",
        "translation": "Sengliang said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a09_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此第二難。",
        "translation": "\"This is the second difficulty.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a09_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "明虛行不應得實報也。",
        "translation": "It shows that false practices shouldn't lead to real rewards.'",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a09_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "僧宗曰。",
        "translation": "Saṃgha Zong said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a10_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第三重難。",
        "translation": "\"The third serious difficulty.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a10_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以果驗因。",
        "translation": "It's examining the cause with the effect.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a10_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二事相違。",
        "translation": "The two things are at odds.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a10_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "虛實未辨。",
        "translation": "What's real and what's false haven't been discerned.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a10_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "請求解釋也。",
        "translation": "Please seek an explanation.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a11_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言善哉善哉善男子(至)諸佛菩薩真實不虛。",
        "translation": "The Buddha said, \"Good, good, good sons!\" (to) The buddhas and bodhisattvas are true and not false.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a12_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "案。",
        "translation": "Commentary.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a13_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "僧亮曰。",
        "translation": "Sengliang said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a13_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "初偈說世間慈也。",
        "translation": "\"The first verse says 'worldly kindness.'",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a13_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "行人以施是實行。",
        "translation": "It's the practice of giving as a means of livelihood for pedestrians.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a13_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "故以施福。",
        "translation": "Therefore, they use the merit of generosity.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a14_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "脩世間慈。",
        "translation": "It's cultivating worldly kindness.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a14_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不及其一況出世間也。",
        "translation": "It's not the same as going beyond the world in one situation.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a14_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何者。",
        "translation": "Why is that?",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a15_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "雖慈一人。",
        "translation": "Even though it's kind to one person.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a15_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "與世之樂。",
        "translation": "It's just like the pleasures of the world.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a15_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "施不得爾。",
        "translation": "They can't bestow it.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a15_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "昇降可知矣。",
        "translation": "Their ascension and descent can be understood.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a16_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "僧宗曰。",
        "translation": "The Saṃgha School said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a16_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "就此明慈有實益門中。",
        "translation": "\"In this approach, we're explaining that compassion has real benefits.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a16_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有五翻為證也。",
        "translation": "There are five explanations that stand as proof.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a17_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "初明脩慈實能轉境。",
        "translation": "First, it shows that cultivating kindness can really transform objects.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a17_16",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第二明慈能斷煩惱。",
        "translation": "Second, it shows that kindness can stop afflictions.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a17_17",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第三明慈為萬善根本。",
        "translation": "Third, it's explained that kindness is the root of all goodness.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a18_18",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第四明慈即萬行。",
        "translation": "Fourth, it shows that kindness is the root of all good actions.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a18_19",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第五引果地之慈。",
        "translation": "The fifth invokes kindness in the stage of fruition.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a19_20",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "證真實不虛也。",
        "translation": "It's the realization that what's true and real isn't false.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a19_21",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛是窮慈之極。",
        "translation": "The Buddha is the ultimate in exhaustive kindness.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a20_22",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "得知因地亦有實益也。",
        "translation": "He can know that there's real benefit in the causal stage as well.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a20_23",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "雖可有此五翻。",
        "translation": "Although these five explanations may exist, if someone wants to address the three questions.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a20_24",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若欲對向三問者。",
        "translation": "Suppose someone wants to address the three questions.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a21_25",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此五翻悉證慈有實益。",
        "translation": "These five explanations all testify that kindness has real benefit.'",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a21_26",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "並答初問。",
        "translation": "They also answer the first question.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a22_27",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "下當更題。",
        "translation": "They'll be followed by another question.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a22_28",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第二問出別答也。",
        "translation": "\"The second question is answered separately.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a22_29",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此偈言。",
        "translation": "The verse says.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a23_30",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "慈之功用。",
        "translation": "\"The merit of kindness ...",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a23_31",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃於諸行為勝。",
        "translation": "It's superior to all practices.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a23_32",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "豈但實益而已。",
        "translation": "Is it not just a real benefit?",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a23_33",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不可以聲聞是虛。",
        "translation": "It's not acceptable for śrāvakas to be vain.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a24_34",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "令菩薩益虛也。",
        "translation": "It causes bodhisattvas to benefit the void.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a24_35",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二問既釋。",
        "translation": "After explaining the second question, the third question is naturally explained.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a25_36",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "則第三問自然釋矣。",
        "translation": "Then the third question is naturally explained.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a25_37",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "寶亮曰。",
        "translation": "Baoliang said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a25_38",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛將答難。",
        "translation": "\"The Buddha will answer this difficult question.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a26_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "先歎之也。",
        "translation": "He'll first praise it.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a26_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "偈明實益格量功德。",
        "translation": "The verse explains that the benefits are truly substantial and meritorious.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a26_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何者。",
        "translation": "Why is that?",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a27_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有人止於一人邊與慈。",
        "translation": "A person stops at the side of one person and shows compassion.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a27_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "欲與其樂。",
        "translation": "They want to share their happiness.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a27_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "始終必得出生死也。",
        "translation": "In the beginning and end, they'll surely escape birth and death.'",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a27_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "答人雖復供養無量五通神仙。",
        "translation": "Answerers, even though a person makes offerings to measureless gods and sages of the five supernormal powers.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a28_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以為福田。",
        "translation": "They think of it as a field of merit.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a29_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不如於一人邊起慈。",
        "translation": "It's not as good as generating kindness at the side of one person.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a29_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十六分中之一也。",
        "translation": "That's one of the sixteen parts.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497a29_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "供養仙人。",
        "translation": "Making offerings to an immortal.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497b01_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃得生死之報。",
        "translation": "Only then will he reap the rewards of birth-and-death.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497b01_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若拔一人苦。",
        "translation": "If he were to remove one person's suffering, he'd really attain the benefits of transcendence.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497b01_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "實獲出世之利也。",
        "translation": "He'll really attain supramundane benefits.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497b02_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又化無量人。",
        "translation": "He also transforms measureless people.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497b02_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "得出於生死。",
        "translation": "They'll attain escape from birth-and-death.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497b02_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知慈是實也。",
        "translation": "You should know that kindness is real.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497b03_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "釋慈有實益之義。",
        "translation": "Explaining kindness has the meaning of real benefit.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497b03_15",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "文齊於此。",
        "translation": "The text is the same here.",
        "source": "T37n1763_037:0497b03_16",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
